        <item>
            <title>香港科技园公司与 UBS 展开合作提供展示平台　连接初创与潜在客户「说好香港科研故事」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/ubs-cooperate-with-hkstp-provide-showcase-platform/people-interview/ppl_interview/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ubs-cooperate-with-hkstp-provide-showcase-platform</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/ubs-cooperate-with-hkstp-provide-showcase-platform/people-interview/ppl_interview/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 09:29:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人物专访]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[业界专访]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[HKSTP]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[UBS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[香港科技园公司]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1208813</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近年社会一直在说「说好香港故事」，而在科研上，大家平常可能在新闻一直看到外国甚么甚么企业又成功研发哪种哪种新技术，其实在香港亦有不少初创企业一直在默默耕耘，在各领域研发不同的新科技以改善人类社会。UBS 日前就宣布与香港科技园公司（科技园公司）展开合作，希望藉著旗下的数码中心，将香港建构成为真正的世界科研中心。</p><h2>初创需要「转折」以求成功</h2><p>在发布会中，科技园公司行政总裁黄克强就表示，在世上 70% 的初创企业都是失败收场，而如果他们要成功，他们需要有人提供「关键转折（Pivot）」的协助，令他们将研发出来的技术，「扭一扭」做出更符合市场需求的产品，令成品可以商品化并赚取利润。今次与 UBS 瑞银的合作，就是希望可以帮助剩余的 30% 初创达至成功。而瑞银财富管理亚洲区主席兼瑞银香港区主管及行政总裁卢彩云亦表示，在这次与科技园公司的合作中，他们会提供旗下位于尖沙咀的数码中心（The Digital Hub），让科技园公司的初创企业展示他们的科研成果，UBS 则会充当超级连系人（Super Connector）的角色，将初创科技企业与企业家、学术人员、策略性合作伙伴及投资者连结在一起。透过这次合作，UBS 及科技园公司希望可以为科技园公司旗下的科企提供更好的培育环境，令这些科企的成品「可落地」，甚至可为初创公司提供一站式服务，例如：与瑞银投行合作为初创公司筹组上市，最终令香港成为其中一个拥有世界科研中心的城市。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208816 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲UBS 瑞银日前与科技园公司举行联合发布会，宣布将会展开合作，为科技园公司旗下初创企业提供展示平台，希望可连接初创与潜在客户，而当日亦有不少科技园公司初创企业参与。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208817 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲科技园公司行政总裁黄克强在发布会中表示，初创要成功一定要有人或机构提供「关键转折（Pivot）」协助，令他们将研发出来的技术，「扭一扭」做出更符合市场需求的产品，令成品可以商品化并赚取利润，这亦是今次他们与 UBS 合作希望达到的成果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1211090 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/403405541_1467492680484888_4049132474191661816_n-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/403405541_1467492680484888_4049132474191661816_n-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/403405541_1467492680484888_4049132474191661816_n-506x900.jpg 506w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/403405541_1467492680484888_4049132474191661816_n-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/403405541_1467492680484888_4049132474191661816_n-864x1536.jpg 864w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/403405541_1467492680484888_4049132474191661816_n.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲瑞银财富管理亚洲区主席兼瑞银香港区主管及行政总裁卢彩云亦表示，在今次合作中，UBS 会充当超级连系人（Super Connector）的角色，将初创科技企业与企业家、学术人员、策略性合作伙伴及投资者连结在一起。UBS 及科技园公司希望透过这次合作，可以为科技园公司旗下的科企提供更好的培育环境，令这些科企的成品「可落地」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208841 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲UBS 旗下的数码中心（The Digital Hub）设有一块极大的展示墙，初创企业在向潜在客户展示产品时可以善加利用。</p><h2>多间初创分享研发成果　不少已商品化解决市场需要</h2><p>而在发布会当日，科技园公司就邀请了多间落户在科技园公司的本地初创企业，趁机分享他们的研发成果，当中不少更加入了近年大热的人工智能（AI）元素，例如：有迎合近年大众注重衞生而设的便携版远紫外光灭菌器及智能通风管净化器、用于快速了解客户脱发问题的仪器、30 秒一扫即可初步了解身体健康状况的装置、由布料出发为消费者带来更舒适兼有实际用效的服装、甚至为长期痛病患者提供根治方案的医疗用产品亦有。当中不少更已商品化并已推出市场，例如：推出智能通风管净化器的企业 LR IOT 就表示已内置在不少由市建局重建的新楼宇、提供 30 秒一扫了解身体状况的 Panoptic AI 公司更已将产品应用在不少私营医院，他们的 CEO 及创办人黄君朗更表示此产品正等待获得 FDA 认证，未来更会与其他机构，例如：保险公司推广此产品，更有可能会推展至位于大湾区或东南亚的机构。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208820 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208821 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208822 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在发布会当中，有不少初创企业亦有展示他们的科研成果，例如：上图这款由 Panoptic AI 公司研发的装置 Vitals，就可以使用平板或拥有镜头的装置，只需短短 30 秒就可透过扫描用家面部皮下的血液流动提取生理数据，之后就会在短时间提供全面的初步健康分析报告。他们的 CEO 兼创办人黄君朗表示 Vitals 正等待 FDA 认证，而现在已获多间本地私营医院采用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208823 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208824 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而另一间展示成品的企业 Dr.Rock，他们的总经理王建镇就展示了他们为长期痛症患者设计，内含独特中国天热稀土（红砭石）及石墨烯的产品，据王氏表示红砭石会发出对身体就有效的远红外线，可与细胞产生同频共震，有助活化细胞、促进血液循环、放松肌肉及恢复体能，更对舒缓及根治痛症很有帮助。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208835 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208825 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208826 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而他们的产品不只有美容枪、按摩枪，温阳百变垫专业板更可创造适当的磁场环境，帮助人体自愈。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208827 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208828 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另一间名为 Comfiknit 亦在现场展出采用独特布料的衣服，他们最新研发出这款拥有保湿功能的布料，可将一定程度的水气保留在皮肤上，对于舒缓困扰不少港人的湿疹有很大帮助，穿著乘搭飞机亦十分舒服。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208829 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208830 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另一间展示研发成果的本地初创 LR IOT，他们现场就展示了这款获市建局赞助开发的 UV-C VentGuard 智能通风管净化器，可以有效切断天井传播链，为家居提供更安心及衞生的环境，而这成品已获市建局安装于旗下不少重建项目，可说已成功「落地」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208831 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲LR IOT 亦表示他们下一步将会为建筑业研发为高空工作工人而设的安全设备，万一有工人未有穿戴合适防护工具，中央管理平台就会收到警告，方便建筑公司及时提醒工人要系好安全带，最大程度避免悲剧发生。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208832 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208833 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而这件由 ERGO 222 展出的 XOne 222 纳米远紫外光灭菌器，就可以在短时间为用家进行消毒，可有效杀灭 99.9% 冠状病毒，而且体积细小，充满一次电亦可使用 4 小时，确实十分实用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208836 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208837 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲此外，相信大家也十分熟悉的本地头发护理企业「发再生」（HairCoSys）亦有展示他们的 AI 护发方案，可以短时间为客户进行 AI 头发头皮分析，再透过 AI 进行产品服务配对，希望为用家找出最佳的头发护理方案。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/ubs-cooperate-with-hkstp-provide-showcase-platform/people-interview/ppl_interview/">香港科技园公司与 UBS 展开合作提供展示平台　连接初创与潜在客户「说好香港科研故事」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
