            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1212831</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>现时科技发达，即使不是航空塔工作人员也可以到 <a href="https://www.liveatc.net/">LiveATC</a> 这类空中通讯追踪网站收听飞机与地面控制塔之间的对话。最近就有人听到羽田空难时 JL516 与羽田航空塔的对话内容，而根据录音内容，JL516 航班已获羽田机场准许降落。</p><p>日本时间 1 月 2 日羽田机场一架载有近 400 名乘客及机组人员的日航客机降落时与日本海上保安厅飞机定翼机相撞，事件中 5 名海上保安厅机组人员罹难，以及近廿名乘客受伤。日航方面表示已接到降落通知，其后亦再度确认，方开始降落。</p><p>日本时间 1 月 2 日下午 5 时 43 分，地面航空塔人员通知 JL516 可继续飞往日本东京羽田机场，随后约 1 分半钟， LiveATC.net 公布的录音显示 JL516 获批准降落，顷刻后航空塔指示 JA722A（海上保安厅的定翼机）滑行至跑道 C-5 （Charlie-5）位置等候，但 JA722A 未有回应航空塔的要求，之后两机都没有再于无线电对话里出现，大约 1 分半钟后， JL131 向航空塔汇报表示机场 34R 跑道位置发生火灾。</p><p>以下影片的 15:02 可听见航空塔允许 JL516 降落（JL516 Cleared to land 34R, Japan Air516）</p><p>15:13 可听到航空塔指示海保厅定翼机滑行至跑道 C5 位置（JA772A，Tokyo TWR Good evening, No.1, Taxi to Holding Point C-5）</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_87940"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LP1xWcyKBDs?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212835" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/170425374272329_P28640443-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/170425374272329_P28640443-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/170425374272329_P28640443-768x510.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/170425374272329_P28640443.jpg 1049w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲日航 JL516 机身起火燃烧，图片来源：<a href="https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/7681715">udn</a></p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr">闻き取れた人の耳によると⇒<br />【RJTT-Twr-TCA-Gnd-Jan-02-2024-0830Z.mp3】<br />&#8211; <a href="https://t.co/3H9CWrmScF">https://t.co/3H9CWrmScF</a><br />&#8211; <a href="https://t.co/CQhOdPeqZT">https://t.co/CQhOdPeqZT</a><br />15:02 JL516「Cleared to land 34 Right, Japanair 516」<br />15:13 Twr「Juliet Alpha 722 Alpha, Tokyo Tower good evening, number 1 taxi to holding point Charlie 5」 <a href="https://t.co/gomnWpVxfc">pic.twitter.com/gomnWpVxfc</a></p><p>&mdash; smcGO (@SMC_Osaka) <a href="https://twitter.com/SMC_Osaka/status/1742255662506352974?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 2, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>日航昨晚（2 日）召开记者会表示，旗下 516 航班在获得地面航空塔许可后才降落，日航常务董事青木纪正亦就事件向大众致歉，但其就认为是次事故主因应该是与航空塔沟通不足所致，但由于事件尚在调查阶段，不会再作太多评论。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212892" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/live2-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/live2-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/live2-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/live2-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/live2.png 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲跑道上的残骸，图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fqj5C-FswQk&amp;ab_channel=ANNnewsCH">ANNnewsCH@YouTube</a></p><p>日本放送协会（NHK）报道指，日本运输安全委员会将会调派 6 名航空事故调查官今日起正式展开羽田机场相撞事故的调查。据报日本国土交通省亦确认灾难发生前，航空塔人员曾经允许日航客机降落跑道，另一方面亦指示海上保安厅控制飞机滑行至跑道。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212893" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/live1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/live1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/live1-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/live1-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/live1.png 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲涉事的 A350-941 残骸，图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fqj5C-FswQk&amp;ab_channel=ANNnewsCH">ANNnewsCH@YouTube</a></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_84165"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Fqj5C-FswQk?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://udn.com/news/story/123877/7682372">udn</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fqj5C-FswQk&amp;ab_channel=ANNnewsCH">ANNnewsCH@YouTube</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/SMC_Osaka/status/174225566250635297">SMC_Osaka@X</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/2024-haneda-airport-runway-collision/fun-tech/">羽田空难航空塔录音 LiveATC 曝光    1）日航允许降落 2）海保于 C5 等候</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
